I give this 1 star because when I downloaded this app my dog🐕 suddenly started to transform into a powerhouse of the cell and ran away🦠. I tried to run after it but then Michael Jackson rose from my driveway and started singing Billie jean while moonwalking.🙈 then when I turned around mr Sliding wig with a very orange tan was being me looking like a centaur with how he stands🐴. He was being very inappropriate trying to force Cheetos down my throat. He then galloped into the street and got hit by Thomas the train. Would not recommend. 🧚🏾🧚🏻‍♂️🧚🏻‍♂️🧜🏾👃🏾👁👄😻😼🙀😹😨🤔🤫🥵😩🤔😦😖😔🙃🙃😜👤🧒🏾🧑🏼‍🦯👨🏼‍🦽🕴🏻👯‍♂️✨🌈☀️🌨
